Plot price

In [38]:
def plot_hist(df,col,bin):
    sns.set(style="white", palette="muted", color_codes=True)
    plt.figure(figsize=(16,7))
    #ax=plt.subplots(figsize=(6,3))
    plt.subplot(1, 2, 1)
    plt.title('Histgram of '+col)
    sns.distplot(df[col], color="m", kde_kws={"shade": True}, bins=bin);
    plt.subplot(1, 2, 2)
    plt.title('Histgram of '+col +' (After removal of outlier)')
    sns.distplot(df[df[col]<3*df[col].std()][col], color="m", kde_kws={"shade": True}, bins=bin);
